title: [Western Waterway, Open Depths]
description: Green into teal into blue into grey, the water rushes east in a patterned current.  Sky meets sea, providing a further palette of blues and blacks and greys.  There is no calm, but the water is rhythmic in its quick movement, almost lulling into a false sense of peace.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, south, southwest, west
